    "description": [
      "Bits of tattered cloth torn from the clothing of passersby indicate the narrow gaps through the bittersweet vines surrounding this grove.  The crab apple trees groan under the weight of these unwelcome guests, which steal the best of rain and sun from their stunted hosts.  The vines twine around every available limb until the grove resembles nothing more than a gargantuan bird's nest."
